divs: Sighting DetailsI was asleep in my bed. At some point I woke up (I don't even remember when) and walked to the front door of my room. I opened the door and saw a gray-colored humanoid with big black eyes. I felt shivering running through my body as well as heat (fear). After that I don't remember anything else, even going back to bed.
